      "role": "user",
      "content": "the lawyer thing is too expensive, i can't even afford a consultation right now. and every time i call the bank they just tell me the same thing about the foreclosure process. i feel like i've tried everything. i'm just looking for a way to actually stop the bleeding and make sure my kids are taken care of, because right now everything i have is just gonna be swallowed up by these creditors. is there any way to actually protect them?",
